{"tid":1537284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不割蓆/不分化/不篤灰 應該加埋 不互屌/不悔氣","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T17:18:24.000Z","uid":60744,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9da6df903ddafe0a907b521354dfe993a38fad5","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"大家係場抗爭都有付出，只差多與少<br />\n<br />\n做咩成日都要屌嚟屌去減自己士氣？<br />\n<br />\n做得唔好可以提點/提醒，但真係好聲氣少少大家士氣都高啲<br />\n<br />\n你睇下對家，班畜聾點仆街點做錯你有冇見過er sir班人渣係記者會屌過佢哋畜聾一句？所以佢哋先愈來愈肆無忌憚<br />\n<br />\n既然大家都為件事好，點解要又屌又盛又成日講悔氣說話令大家難過？<br />\n<br />\n例子 1： <br />\n<br />\n不要說：唔好送頭啦<br />\n<br />\n試著說：如果可以撤退不如撤退先啦<br />\n<br />\n例子 2 ：<br />\n<br />\n不要說 ： 你班和理非係中後排阻撚住我哋呀，又唔還手又唔幫拖屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n試著說 ： 如果開打你哋驚嘅可以早少少散，咁我哋都方便啲走，當然最好可以嘅梗係大家一齊打佢老母<br />\n<br />\n例子 3 ：<br />\n<br />\n不要說 ： 又送頭做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n試著說 ： 我哋仲有大把時間玩，手足係時候轉場啦<br />\n<br />\n我可能講得唔係咁好，但真係期望大家唔好再互屌傷士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e08189a6ec655b9cd09d4c4dd484b1947a85e7","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9376a5fd02499a979b37780ad4217bf9fa8ce893","tid":1537284,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eba72b7c4f1e12ddbe14c8da9553de0b0679f6","tid":1537284,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"同意！<br />\n<br />\n907 再和你塞 908 美領集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆不督灰 唔係口號 要做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534615</a>"},{"pid":"438a086fe66bfbba36de5bdea04839bb428d3a16","tid":1537284,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daa26ac48c99ec1ae177048346b3567e05ea5c37","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0291e46803e6c03162b97086b63199b25aa901a6","tid":1537284,"uid":316967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"Aggee<br />\n對自己手足好啲=對自己好啲"},{"pid":"c16d14814d23365a3dbf191e151dedaf3617a186","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08bcecae472ff0c3c129e55c8eeca985825377cf","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14e9853d3a48b27100fa0727c3d3b83cac664bf5","tid":1537284,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6262d8471bbbeecec53555977b978f5eb56a04e","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8807d699f08b8b0a6fb2b082bfaaa0519dbdc8","tid":1537284,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b9160489af4f6bd61a7a9451bb2e51d8c46085","tid":1537284,"uid":60744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98642297e46043573